    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i’m just hitting a wall with everything. like, i’ve tried looking at the bright side or finding \"meaning\" in the struggle, but it’s all just a lie we tell ourselves to stay busy. there’s no actual point to any of this. just endless entropy and nothingness. it feels more honest to just admit that everything is empty.",
